{"title":"前期准备-Web前端","date":"2023-10-20T13:34:15.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Oct 20, 2023","L":"10/20/2023","MM-DD":"10-20"},"thumbnail":"https://cdn.cco.moe/img/img03.webp","link":"post/webpre","comments":true,"tags":["Web"],"categories":["share"],"updated":"2024-01-11T12:48:52.470Z","content":"<blockquote>\n<p>学长课堂前期准备教程</p>\n</blockquote>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<h2 id=\"一、nodejs安装并配置\">一、nodejs安装并配置<a title=\"#一、nodejs安装并配置\" href=\"#一、nodejs安装并配置\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"(1)-安装\">(1) 安装<a title=\"#(1)-安装\" href=\"#(1)-安装\"></a></h3>\n<p>在nodejs官网 <a href=\"https://nodejs.org/en/download/current\" target=\"_blank\">https://nodejs.org/en/download/current</a> 下载好 <strong>nodejs</strong> 安装包，</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.cco.moe/webpre/05.webp\" alt=\"05\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>注意下载 .msi 版本，并且根据自己电脑cpu架构选择合适的版本，一般下载64-bit。然后打开安装包进行安装，安装路径在 <strong>C:\\Program Files\\nodejs</strong> ，以下的所有组件都勾选：</p>\n<p>安装程序完成后，按下 <strong>win+R</strong> 键，输入 cmd 打开终端，输入以下指令：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sh\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">node -v   <span class=\"comment\"># 查看node版本号</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">npm -v    <span class=\"comment\"># 查看npm版本号</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>如果终端均给出了相应的版本号则说明安装成功：</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.cco.moe/webpre/06.webp\" alt=\"version\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"(2)-环境配置\">(2) 环境配置<a title=\"#(2)-环境配置\" href=\"#(2)-环境配置\"></a></h3>\n<p>使用 <strong>管理员权限❗️❗️</strong> 打开终端，即在开始菜单搜索cmd，然后鼠标右键 <strong>cmd.exe</strong> 以管理员身份运行，然后输入以下命令进入nodejs安装目录(如果没有使用管理员权限打开终端就运行以下代码会出现 <strong>permission denied❗️</strong> )：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sh\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">cd</span> C:\\Program files\\nodejs    <span class=\"comment\"># 进入nodejs目录</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>然后输入以下命令创建全局组件文件夹和缓存文件夹：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sh\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">mkdir</span> node_global  <span class=\"comment\"># 创建全局组件文件夹</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">mkdir</span> node_cache   <span class=\"comment\"># 创建缓存文件夹</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>然后输入以下命令设置npm全局包目录和缓存目录：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sh\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm config <span class=\"built_in\">set</span> prefix <span class=\"string\">&quot;C:\\Program Files\\nodejs\\node_global&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">npm config <span class=\"built_in\">set</span> cache <span class=\"string\">&quot;C:\\Program Files\\nodejs\\node_cache&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>以上操作如果终端没有报错则说明命令执行成功，接下来进行下一步，设置系统环境变量。首先在桌面找到 <em><strong>我的电脑</strong></em> ，选中右键选择 <em><strong>属性</strong></em> ，选择 <em><strong>高级</strong></em> ，然后在底部选择 <em><strong>环境变量</strong></em> ：</p>\n<p>进去后首先修改 <strong>用户变量</strong> ，将环境变量 Path 中的npm路径更换为刚才设置的 <strong>node_global 全局包</strong> 的路径。</p>\n<p>即，将以上红框部分修改为以下路径：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sh\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">C:\\Program Files\\nodejs\\node_global</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>然后点击确定，然后还需要在 <strong>Path</strong> 变量中新建 <code>%NODE_PATH%</code> ,如下图：</p>\n<p>用户变量设置好之后再新建一个系统变量，如图：</p>\n<p>添加以下内容：</p>\n<p>变量名：<code>NODE_PATH</code></p>\n<p>变量值：<code>C:\\Program Files\\nodejs\\node_global\\node_modules</code></p>\n<p>然后点击确定，到此nodejs安装及环境配置完成。</p>\n<h2 id=\"二、vue脚手架创建\">二、Vue脚手架创建<a title=\"#二、vue脚手架创建\" href=\"#二、vue脚手架创建\"></a></h2>\n<p>Vue依赖于nodejs，安装好nodejs之后就可以直接创建Vue脚手架，打开终端，cd到想要使用Vue的项目文件夹中，输入以下命令即可：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sh\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm create vue@latest</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>这一指令将会安装并执行 <a href=\"https://github.com/vuejs/create-vue\" target=\"_blank\">create-vue</a>，它是 Vue 官方的项目脚手架工具。你将会看到一些诸如 TypeScript 和测试支持之类的可选功能提示：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight sh\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">✔ Project name: … &lt;your-project-name&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">✔ Add TypeScript? … No / Yes</span><br><span class=\"line\">✔ Add JSX Support? … No / Yes</span><br><span class=\"line\">✔ Add Vue Router <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> Single Page Application development? … No / Yes</span><br><span class=\"line\">✔ Add Pinia <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> state management? … No / Yes</span><br><span class=\"line\">✔ Add Vitest <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> Unit testing? … No / Yes</span><br><span class=\"line\">✔ Add an End-to-End Testing Solution? … No / Cypress / Playwright</span><br><span class=\"line\">✔ Add ESLint <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> code quality? … No / Yes</span><br><span class=\"line\">✔ Add Prettier <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> code formatting? … No / Yes</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">Scaffolding project <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> ./&lt;your-project-name&gt;...</span><br><span class=\"line\">Done.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>如果不确定是否要开启某个功能，你可以直接按下回车键选择 <strong>No</strong> .</p>\n<h2 id=\"三、vscode汉化\">三、VSCode汉化<a title=\"#三、vscode汉化\" href=\"#三、vscode汉化\"></a></h2>\n<p>在VSCode侧边栏中选择扩展，输入 <strong>Chinese (Simplified) Language Pack for Visual Studio Code</strong> 后回车，然后安装 <strong>重启</strong> 即可实现汉化。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.cco.moe/webpre/07.webp\" alt=\"vscode汉化\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"四、vscode插件推荐\">四、VSCode插件推荐<a title=\"#四、vscode插件推荐\" href=\"#四、vscode插件推荐\"></a></h2>\n<p>HTML CSS Support</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.cco.moe/webpre/04.webp\" alt=\"html css support\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>open in brower</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.cco.moe/webpre/01.webp\" alt=\"open in browser\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>Path Intellisense</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.cco.moe/webpre/03.webp\" alt=\"path intellisense\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>Prettier - Code formatter</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.cco.moe/webpre/02.webp\" alt=\"open in browser\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n","prev":{"title":"日常の笔记","link":"post/note"},"next":{"title":"Homebrewの安装教程","link":"post/homebrewinstall"},"plink":"http://example.com/post/webpre/","toc":[{"id":"一、nodejs安装并配置","title":"一、nodejs安装并配置","index":"1","children":[{"id":"(1)-安装","title":"(1) 安装","index":"1.1"},{"id":"(2)-环境配置","title":"(2) 环境配置","index":"1.2"}]},{"id":"二、vue脚手架创建","title":"二、Vue脚手架创建","index":"2"},{"id":"三、vscode汉化","title":"三、VSCode汉化","index":"3"},{"id":"四、vscode插件推荐","title":"四、VSCode插件推荐","index":"4"}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"chromoe","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\\\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\\\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","published":"October 20, 2023"},"reading_time":"889 words in 6 min"}